{"tid":448183,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［live]一個人又有咩好怕喎之生日毒遊老鼠樂園","createTime":"2017-10-26T03:54:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T10:03:39.000Z","uid":5802,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6b4cb4b6975475743fd160ccd4727a7979de3d20","tid":448183,"uid":5802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T03:54:01.000Z","msg":"是咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鑑於前幾日見到佢地出門票優惠plan<br />\n600幾就可以入場玩兩次<br />\n完全岩曬我呢啲成世人都唔會去<br />\n所以唔會特登俾咁貴去買咩證物證<br />\n但偶爾又屎忽痕咁想去既毒丁<br />\n再加上生日咁岩係個期限入面 <br />\n一於就決定買飛入去玩一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個post純粹係個紀錄帖俾自己留個紀念<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">同埋正日係29號 不過個日係番工去唔到<br />\n都好既 起碼唔使一丁友咁過先</span><br />\n所以就趁今日放假去當提早慶祝"},{"pid":"fd4c94c227b11d9c5e9545411df0ab5c9f40a26e","tid":448183,"uid":5802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T03:56:20.000Z","msg":"正所謂去迪迪尼要做足準備<br />\n執咗一個似乎超爆炸既尿袋 少少零食 一樽水同其他野入背囊<br />\n始終入去玩成日 懶得拎太多野<br />\n鑑於佢地好似唔俾拎野食入去園區<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/115603_110e9ab6452453db98ff02f0688c87b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F115603_110e9ab6452453db98ff02f0688c87b0.jpg&h=c4ae0a06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又窮又大食既我會係出面食番個靚早餐<br />\n平<br />\n食到飽飽先入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鬼叫入面啲野又貴又細份 慳得一餐得一餐<br />\n仲特登dl鬼埋佢個鴨屎 <br />\n到時候慳番啲時間去排隊<br />\n同埋知道啲活動時間 到時候霸定個靚位"},{"pid":"9e66261c32b304177ed8e30bd8df190e44a0269b","tid":448183,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T03:57:00.000Z","msg":"啲零食會唔會入去之前俾人扔咗"},{"pid":"ae463e6a3d80aa9867cf22a926fe5a723963a39d","tid":448183,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T03:58:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鑑於前幾日見到佢地出門票優惠plan<br />\n600幾就可以入場玩兩次<br />\n完全岩曬我呢啲成世人都唔會去<br />\n所以唔會特登俾咁貴去買咩證物證<br />\n但偶爾又屎忽痕咁想去既毒丁<br />\n再加上生日咁岩係個期限入面 <br />\n一於就決定買飛入去玩一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個post純粹係個紀錄帖俾自己留個紀念<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">同埋正日係29號 不過個日係番工去唔到<br />\n都好既 起碼唔使一丁友咁過先</span><br />\n所以就趁今日放假去當提早慶祝</blockquote><br />\n男人老狗一個去老鼠公園我唔知有乜好玩，留名學野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n祝你生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"931d6ed8c8dc49b2f233377bc4314fb22bc202dc","tid":448183,"uid":5802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T03:59:06.000Z","msg":"由於時間關係 我已經到咗<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/115856_0b3dc1fa7910af439984a679c0582eec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F115856_0b3dc1fa7910af439984a679c0582eec.jpg&h=df4081ad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/115857_772b0d3d83ed63a7bda89ba00158da27.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F115857_772b0d3d83ed63a7bda89ba00158da27.jpg&h=d479f641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢張好明顯係鳩影<br />\n個太陽大到我都唔知影咗啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇番資料佢好似十點就開放入場<br />\n如果想霸頭位玩的話係應該十點前去到<br />\n但對黎我黎講係訓覺重要啲<br />\n同埋我係黎玩 只會去啲自己有興趣既項目<br />\n而唔係每樣項目都好似做任務咁樣全部去曬<br />\n輕鬆啲啦 香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b7ce6f82b48ff9b1df22e1c084eccfc88756fc2","tid":448183,"uid":89433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:01:52.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f6ef081a94ec4674268a15d438bdde476fe174","tid":448183,"uid":5802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:04:44.000Z","msg":"唉 前兩日係網上買飛個時唔小心打咗自己個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到對唔到身份入場<br />\n但個日已經打咗去客服 個邊話幫我搞掂<br />\n到時候就咁入場就得<br />\n但結果今日都係對唔到身份 要另外再排隊整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b867f9aedc81c0e87465d44facabca2e399bd4bd","tid":448183,"uid":5802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:07:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲零食會唔會入去之前俾人扔咗</blockquote><br />\n冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲包啊餅啊都仲係度<br />\n仲有拎多杯咖啡入去tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我前面個啊姐個飯團反而過唔到關<br />\n俾食蕉彈番出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a904d9e86e2b2d0fe9f0e96844bfaeb1ff1f1652","tid":448183,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:08:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唉 前兩日係網上買飛個時唔小心打咗自己個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到對唔到身份入場<br />\n但個日已經打咗去客服 個邊話幫我搞掂<br />\n到時候就咁入場就得<br />\n但結果今日都係對唔到身份 要另外再排隊整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打自己名唔得，打乜先得，飛機？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1936667dc42cac588e480517677a3c85efc0c72e","tid":448183,"uid":90802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:10:05.000Z","msg":"毒撚留名待去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"281880de366b480ba4cf0acfa8e0d28d23f04fad","tid":448183,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:17:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唉 前兩日係網上買飛個時唔小心打咗自己個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到對唔到身份入場<br />\n但個日已經打咗去客服 個邊話幫我搞掂<br />\n到時候就咁入場就得<br />\n但結果今日都係對唔到身份 要另外再排隊整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打自己名唔得，打乜先得，飛機？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢應該係打錯自己個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n毒撚真係自己個名都可以打錯"},{"pid":"98950f4e4b1c9776ad9dcc4ecd8c45f3554b27c5","tid":448183,"uid":8647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:17:12.000Z","msg":"生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b96987c233b81a2b768eede10a51f53c6ec2981","tid":448183,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:19:21.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好玩小小世界<br />\n伏到仆街"},{"pid":"666333f4de7ed52b94311f088369dcb8c867b50f","tid":448183,"uid":5802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:22:18.000Z","msg":"最後我係成功入場既<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/122157_971013e3847187f7ede7df9abbb02d24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F122157_971013e3847187f7ede7df9abbb02d24.jpg&h=f14669b3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/122158_81e1e1a4cc0a7d62d2213096c2f91efa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F122158_81e1e1a4cc0a7d62d2213096c2f91efa.jpg&h=80c3af8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同埋勁好彩咁影到架飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba2a4c7d6cb1b772f538658539a02eba78f27ab1","tid":448183,"uid":5802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:24:13.000Z","msg":"依家就去玩呢個唔知乜葫蘆串串飛船<br />\n其實都有啲淆 因為我好驚離心力<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/122409_9774ac1e92804bcfe972bdccad45f6a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F122409_9774ac1e92804bcfe972bdccad45f6a9.jpg&h=c8d7c6dd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/122410_5a3790760c914411ccea0113f7e8b38a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F122410_5a3790760c914411ccea0113f7e8b38a.jpg&h=d6b3fe4a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b46a43f79b77bb7ba5faa0a4d07a545410fd493c","tid":448183,"uid":5802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:24:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唉 前兩日係網上買飛個時唔小心打咗自己個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到對唔到身份入場<br />\n但個日已經打咗去客服 個邊話幫我搞掂<br />\n到時候就咁入場就得<br />\n但結果今日都係對唔到身份 要另外再排隊整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打自己名唔得，打乜先得，飛機？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢應該係打錯自己個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n毒撚真係自己個名都可以打錯</blockquote><br />\n其實係個輸入法自動幫我改咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f4a59d3687f87e0cb7a42c4f0e48443bb7566d","tid":448183,"uid":5802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:25:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>千祈唔好玩小小世界<br />\n伏到仆街</blockquote><br />\n唔係掛<br />\n原本都有啲想去呢個<br />\nBtw多謝提醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e4ba3f3ba26495abfeb2b24e697f9f49d70ca0","tid":448183,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:26:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家就去玩呢個唔知乜葫蘆串串飛船<br />\n其實都有啲淆 因為我好驚離心力<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/122409_9774ac1e92804bcfe972bdccad45f6a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F122409_9774ac1e92804bcfe972bdccad45f6a9.jpg&h=c8d7c6dd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/122410_5a3790760c914411ccea0113f7e8b38a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F122410_5a3790760c914411ccea0113f7e8b38a.jpg&h=d6b3fe4a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個咩嚟"},{"pid":"860b677504d6c56f38d6fd328d49ca04ddfc7d22","tid":448183,"uid":44267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:29:33.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"bff700b07f5ce92a837b6316998611589d938e83","tid":448183,"uid":5802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:53:05.000Z","msg":"更正頭先玩個個名係 太空飛船<br />\n其實好簡單咁升起轉30秒左右<br />\n毒丁福音 一人坐曬成架<br />\n一坐落去個船 我覺得我後欄都要起火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/125025_ba3860c290fdaebc9d8ffa58378f2234.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F125025_ba3860c290fdaebc9d8ffa58378f2234.jpg&h=07971d8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我覺得我好似幫前面個爸爸影寫真咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n玩完呢個就去咗探_大大<br />\n但因為太多人去朝聖我地偉大既_大大<br />\n所以我拎咗飛陣間再番去<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/125303_6adb95eabaef661dd71309a774e62b3f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F125303_6adb95eabaef661dd71309a774e62b3f.jpg&h=161c8285&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f3525393a81650f6678659ef7c2e0607c47192c","tid":448183,"uid":5802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T05:15:22.000Z","msg":"基於無聊既關係去咗摺個糖果盒<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/131506_f307f876f36b58e8bdbf8e6edb3929f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F131506_f307f876f36b58e8bdbf8e6edb3929f0.jpg&h=2455680e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拎啲裝我啲零食都好<br />\n順便拎咗幾粒糖<br />\n依家就去緊有巴打話伏既小小世界<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/131520_581143cb81d04f65420d6aa9263788df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F131520_581143cb81d04f65420d6aa9263788df.jpg&h=bf8e4a80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n玩完呢個應該差不多時間番去搵_大大"},{"pid":"80c694146283cc387d102222af91dc846e4f06c1","tid":448183,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T05:17:53.000Z","msg":"小小世界真係無聊到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e8d9fac886eb3fb679a90ffb0668898bca0eabc","tid":448183,"uid":98961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T05:18:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a790b9bf6f05a275a38c5580d7e1a5f1a85ff06","tid":448183,"uid":5802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T05:27:25.000Z","msg":"不聽巴打言 吃虧在眼前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來真係好無聊<br />\n就咗坐係架船上面兜一個圈<br />\n然後隔離兩邊有啲好似中曬幅射既公仔係度郁身郁世就冇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/132657_2355af1de50c465fc1d2484880a177ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F132657_2355af1de50c465fc1d2484880a177ad.jpg&h=6021023e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全場我覺得得意既居然係呢班自轉企鵝<br />\n呢張圖就咁睇佢地好似啲邪教係度做緊啲咩祟拜儀式咁<br />\n仲要有個太陽係中間<br />\n不過行得耐當咗船河抖吓都okay既<br />\n要排隊入去就不了啦"},{"pid":"b76d8bd6d717a3328482432c9e5bcb0337a6dc75","tid":448183,"uid":5802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T05:47:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 突發 有女！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/134538_6c584480090152e56046331051c9f4c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F134538_6c584480090152e56046331051c9f4c4.jpg&h=33236ef5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/134541_bbf5287a6676dd16989b8015e5aaf81c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F134541_bbf5287a6676dd16989b8015e5aaf81c.jpg&h=187e1da6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成車最靚個個係睡公主<br />\n但可惜我影唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/134629_0f2462be08043f35e0ec4613765b8c37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F134629_0f2462be08043f35e0ec4613765b8c37.jpg&h=df21687b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/134631_df26b1e9bcb864c0e5115bbd7b092b49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F134631_df26b1e9bcb864c0e5115bbd7b092b49.jpg&h=afa8aea3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去到個時個巡遊都差不多就完<br />\n所以都係睇得個幾架"}]}